  <text xml:id="_1-SiLayakh.text.7">
    <meta tag="title">7 - Pekhistiwe Keji </meta>
    <meta tag="source">Herman</meta>
    <comment tag="date-created"></comment>
    <comment tag="date-modified"></comment>
    <comment>This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.</comment>
